ervices …   conserve your cash flow  no down payment options you can acquire the equipment with no down payment we can book loans and lease transactions with no cash down  save your current bank lines of credit by using rev financial services your business can keep its current bank lines of credit for growth projects and other investments  manage your cash flow with rev financial services our financing options let you schedule your payments to fit changes in your cash flow for companies with contract and seasonal cash flow fluctuations your financing contract can be structured to provide stepup or stepdown payments we also can schedule your contract with skip payments during slow months or plan annual semiannual quarterly or monthly payments   flexible equipment financing programs  flexible payment schedules take advantage of flexible payment schedules to allow for seasonality in your business or contracts we have financial solutions to suit any scenario  endofterm options at rev financial services you can choose a number of contract term end equipment options we can schedule a walkaway lease on your equipment purchase simply operate the equipment during term and then turn in the equipment at lease end  application process we offer applicationonly approvals up to k credit approval is quick and easy   more rev financial service benefits  keep your equipment updated keeping your fleet updated with the latest options and technological advances can give you a decided edge in this competitive market by working with rev financial services you can upgrade to new and better equipment during or at the end of the equipment contract term  tax benefits depending on whether you are financing through a lease or a loan product your payments may be treated as a fully deductible operating expense or you may depreciate the equipment these deductions can reduce your tax liability apply now for financing or leasing apply now or request a quote learn more contact us  shuttle school bus 