y duty vehicle construction” peters added “the addition of ferrara to the rev fire group enables a number of new growth opportunities including expansion of our reach nationwide and adding new geographical regions and key accounts we look forward to building upon the success of the ferrara brand with an emphasis on driving new product innovation and exceeding customers’ expectations”“we are extremely pleased to have ferrara fire apparatus join our team at rev ferrara further strengthens our brand offering of fire apparatus vehicles and market presence adding a diverse product portfolio that is complementary to our line of great americanmade specialty vehicles tim sullivan ceo rev group inc said ferrara will immediately contribute strategic value by expanding the rev fire group national footprint dealer sales network service and aftermarket parts revenue as well as enhancing our robust line of custom chassis and aerial products for multiple market segments”headquartered in holden la ferrara employs more than  employees with annual revenue of approximately  million the acquisition of ferrara fire apparatus inc closed on april   contemporaneous with the acquisition rev has refinanced its debt facilities to include a new  million asset based lending abl revolving credit facility and a  million year term loan details are available in the k filed today with the sec tags fire apparatus join the discussion the comments below are membergenerated and do not necessarily reflect the opinions of firerescuecom or its staff if you cannot see comments try disabling privacy and ad blocking plugins in your browser all comments must comply with our member commenting policy fire apparatus buyers guide how to buy fire apparatus a watershed year for doitall vehicles safety a concern as tankers become combination units repair or replace financial factors for apparatus more product news latest product news fri  quick take unmanned aircraft systems in the fire service fit for duty how to be